{"title":"如何成为AI-native设计师？","slug":"qwqgo4gwbhbs9e6f","summary":"如果抛开用户调研和产品定义不谈，之前设计师的核心工作始终如一：画图。画线框图、做视觉规范——把它们交接给研发，然后漫长地等待。 从本质上讲，我曾经就是一个“翻译官”。 把需求翻译成创意，把创意翻译成设计文件，然后再等着别人把这些文件翻译成代码。 这一切在 2024 年发生了改变。","category":"PART3️⃣ 产品设计师AI能力矩阵","tags":["PART3️⃣ 产品设计师AI能力矩阵"],"featured":false,"order":50,"level":1,"updatedAt":"2026-04-23","wordCount":3780,"sourceUrl":"https://www.yuque.com/abyssalsailor/yg90qa/qwqgo4gwbhbs9e6f","html":"<p data-lake-id=\"ub090ddc9\" id=\"ub090ddc9\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc8534dc4\" id=\"uc8534dc4\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">如果抛开用户调研和产品定义不谈，之前设计师的核心工作始终如一：画图。画线框图、做视觉规范——把它们交接给研发，然后漫长地等待。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u2f7e681e\" id=\"u2f7e681e\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc834bced\" id=\"uc834bced\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">从本质上讲，我曾经就是一个“翻译官”。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u308e5438\" id=\"u308e5438\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub70ffb25\" id=\"ub70ffb25\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">把需求翻译成创意，把创意翻译成设计文件，然后再等着别人把这些文件翻译成代码。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u104c2cc4\" id=\"u104c2cc4\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1776950770991-4f989c20-82d0-48fb-9cec-2a0e65219832.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u32929767-e364-49f8-9e53-0b2924a81e1%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22ud56835bc-3d36-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A700%2C%22height%22%3A181%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A89315%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1400%2C%22originHeight%22%3A361%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22ENGINEERING%20RESEARCH%20NEEDS%20DESIGN%20MOCKUP%20LDEA%20CODE%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A981%2C%22y%22%3A147%2C%22width%22%3A103%2C%22height%22%3A22%2C%22text%22%3A%22ENGINEERING%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A308%2C%22y%22%3A147%2C%22width%22%3A83%2C%22height%22%3A23%2C%22text%22%3A%22RESEARCH%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A96%2C%22y%22%3A148%2C%22width%22%3A164%2C%22height%22%3A52%2C%22text%22%3A%22NEEDS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A611%2C%22y%22%3A149%2C%22width%22%3A64%2C%22height%22%3A21%2C%22text%22%3A%22DESIGN%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A736%2C%22y%22%3A150%2C%22width%22%3A205%2C%22height%22%3A59%2C%22text%22%3A%22MOCKUP%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A440%2C%22y%22%3A150%2C%22width%22%3A111%2C%22height%22%3A48%2C%22text%22%3A%22LDEA%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1123%2C%22y%22%3A154%2C%22width%22%3A165%2C%22height%22%3A53%2C%22text%22%3A%22CODE%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23090807%22%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u832e9a3e%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"ua163ce14\" id=\"ua163ce14\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3e43f5aa\" id=\"u3e43f5aa\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">这一切在 2024 年发生了改变。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ue6c30b60\" id=\"ue6c30b60\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufec152e4\" id=\"ufec152e4\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">我现在的主力工具变成了 Claude Code、Figma Make 以及各种大语言模型 (LLMs)。它们从根本上重塑了我的工作方式。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ud9e33ef6\" id=\"ud9e33ef6\"><span data-lake-id=\"u273d6cb4\" id=\"u273d6cb4\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">我不再交付静态的设计稿和 Figma 原型连线，而是直接交付</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u0cede77b\" id=\"u0cede77b\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">可运行的 Demo</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u85277fdb\" id=\"u85277fdb\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">。 我不再去组件库里翻找拼凑，而是将我的设计系统直接接入 Claude Code，让它来生成界面。 我也开始在 ChatGPT 的项目里进行调研和信息整合。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ue3f2340b\" id=\"ue3f2340b\"><span data-lake-id=\"u997bebec\" id=\"u997bebec\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">在这个过程中，我不再是一个翻译官。我更像是一名</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u777b692f\" id=\"u777b692f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">指挥家</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uaa5d3009\" id=\"uaa5d3009\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">：</span><span data-lake-id=\"u523e7a53\" id=\"u523e7a53\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"background-color: #FBDE28\">下达指令，将我的意图和经验转化为 AI 可以执行的任务，然后运用资深设计师的判断力去评估它返回的结果。至于那些最关键的部分，我依然会亲自动手。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u7122bb16\" id=\"u7122bb16\"><span data-lake-id=\"u71976818\" id=\"u71976818\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">七年的经验并没有过时。它们只是转移了阵地。 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u79cfe9a4\" id=\"u79cfe9a4\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">技能本身没有变，只是应用场景变了。</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"ud0a9e410\" id=\"ud0a9e410\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1776950804647-2c531777-da64-420a-b56d-4e4a3fb651e7.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u9716b891-7228-4a8a-94f6-0afe74a08bf%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22ud56835bc-3d36-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A700%2C%22height%22%3A137%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A80836%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1400%2C%22originHeight%22%3A273%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22DESIGN%20TO%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A109%2C%22y%22%3A54%2C%22width%22%3A489%2C%22height%22%3A126%2C%22text%22%3A%22DESIGN%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A649%2C%22y%22%3A76%2C%22width%22%3A120%2C%22height%22%3A103%2C%22text%22%3A%22TO%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%231a0d0c%22%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ub8f515ad%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\"></card></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"suSpW\" id=\"suSpW\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubd639733\" id=\"ubd639733\">一、在代码中培养“设计直觉” (Design Sense)</span></h1><p data-lake-id=\"u4128ad9e\" id=\"u4128ad9e\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc08ac05a\" id=\"uc08ac05a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">设计师们长久以来都有一种特有的挫败感：你能想象出来，但你做不出来。或者更准确地说：你画出来的东西，和最终跑在线上的东西，永远不是一回事。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uc22da9c5\" id=\"uc22da9c5\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1776950818519-4b346d50-263c-4458-b155-1b7e4614b6f9.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u701b005b-30a7-49f6-aa11-0c4e276c4d8%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22ud56835bc-3d36-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A700%2C%22height%22%3A379%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A221987%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1400%2C%22originHeight%22%3A757%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22STATE%20OF%20AL%20UN%20DESIGH%20TOOLS%20TRUE%20POWER%20HERE%20DESIGNER-FRIENDLY%20ZONE%20BOLT%20GEMINI%20W%20WINDSURF%20WONDER%20MAKE%20CLAUDE%20CLAUDE%20LOVABLE%20REPLIT%20MAGIC%20PATTERNS%20COGE%20PROOF-OF-CONCEPT%20MAKER%20APP%20SHIPPER%20LESS%20CODE%20MORE%20CODE%20PX%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A70%2C%22y%22%3A61%2C%22width%22%3A633%2C%22height%22%3A43%2C%22text%22%3A%22STATE%20OF%20AL%20UN%20DESIGH%20TOOLS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1172%2C%22y%22%3A198%2C%22width%22%3A162%2C%22height%22%3A25%2C%22text%22%3A%22TRUE%20POWER%20HERE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A472%2C%22y%22%3A201%2C%22width%22%3A233%2C%22height%22%3A18%2C%22text%22%3A%22DESIGNER-FRIENDLY%20ZONE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A732%2C%22y%22%3A256%2C%22width%22%3A72%2C%22height%22%3A31%2C%22text%22%3A%22BOLT%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A104%2C%22y%22%3A259%2C%22width%22%3A100%2C%22height%22%3A28%2C%22text%22%3A%22GEMINI%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1016%2C%22y%22%3A259%2C%22width%22%3A143%2C%22height%22%3A23%2C%22text%22%3A%22W%20WINDSURF%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A422%2C%22y%22%3A259%2C%22width%22%3A101%2C%22height%22%3A28%2C%22text%22%3A%22WONDER%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A623%2C%22y%22%3A265%2C%22width%22%3A49%2C%22height%22%3A15%2C%22text%22%3A%22MAKE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1237%2C%22y%22%3A311%2C%22width%22%3A86%2C%22height%22%3A25%2C%22text%22%3A%22CLAUDE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A70%2C%22y%22%3A321%2C%22width%22%3A133%2C%22height%22%3A29%2C%22text%22%3A%22CLAUDE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A600%2C%22y%22%3A321%2C%22width%22%3A110%2C%22height%22%3A30%2C%22text%22%3A%22LOVABLE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A987%2C%22y%22%3A321%2C%22width%22%3A94%2C%22height%22%3A26%2C%22text%22%3A%22REPLIT%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A401%2C%22y%22%3A327%2C%22width%22%3A137%2C%22height%22%3A22%2C%22text%22%3A%22MAGIC%20PATTERNS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1240%2C%22y%22%3A340%2C%22width%22%3A59%2C%22height%22%3A20%2C%22text%22%3A%22COGE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A69%2C%22y%22%3A475%2C%22width%22%3A301%2C%22height%22%3A33%2C%22text%22%3A%22PROOF-OF-CONCEPT%20MAKER%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1176%2C%22y%22%3A477%2C%22width%22%3A158%2C%22height%22%3A31%2C%22text%22%3A%22APP%20SHIPPER%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A66%2C%22y%22%3A526%2C%22width%22%3A98%2C%22height%22%3A24%2C%22text%22%3A%22LESS%20CODE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1228%2C%22y%22%3A526%2C%22width%22%3A103%2C%22height%22%3A22%2C%22text%22%3A%22MORE%20CODE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A627%2C%22y%22%3A605%2C%22width%22%3A41%2C%22height%22%3A20%2C%22text%22%3A%22PX%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f7f5f5%22%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u2dd81442%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"ubfc58e25\" id=\"ubfc58e25\"><span data-lake-id=\"uee9088b1\" id=\"uee9088b1\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">Figma 是一个出色的工具。它是一个中间层，它能让你慢下来，强迫你思考。你在里面培养的直觉是</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u368b5def\" id=\"u368b5def\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">空间和视觉上的</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u80471c38\" id=\"u80471c38\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">——你通过拖拽图形来感知变化。这跟在纸上画草图在本质上是一样的。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u4db74012\" id=\"u4db74012\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6ee02d57\" id=\"u6ee02d57\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">但在一个真实的产品中，设计直觉存在于</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1b0cbb2c\" id=\"u1b0cbb2c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">系统和时间维度</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u018cf0ab\" id=\"u018cf0ab\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">中：真实数据涌入时界面如何表现，动画的缓动曲线如何，从一个交互到下一个交互的逻辑链条是怎样的。这完全需要调动另一组“肌肉”。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u22072851\" id=\"u22072851\"><span data-lake-id=\"u51b4eb54\" id=\"u51b4eb54\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">那么，如何才能在代码中培养设计直觉？</span></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"o44Zb\" id=\"o44Zb\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4bed1d6c\" id=\"u4bed1d6c\">外化你的隐性知识 ↘</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u239054d0\" id=\"u239054d0\"><span data-lake-id=\"u898fb9bd\" id=\"u898fb9bd\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"background-color: #FBDE28\">AI 编程极大地降低了跑出“第一版草稿”的成本</span><span data-lake-id=\"ua4751ff1\" id=\"ua4751ff1\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">。现在真正的难点在于：如何生成高质量的“第一版”——然后再基于此进行高效的迭代。这其实考验的是：你是否能将你的</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5b77d049\" id=\"u5b77d049\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">隐性知识</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3e49210a\" id=\"u3e49210a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\"> (Tacit Knowledge) 传递给 AI。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u88d370a1\" id=\"u88d370a1\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue74199a8\" id=\"ue74199a8\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"background-color: #FBDE28\">AI 懂这个世界的显性知识：那些你能 Google 到的东西、写在文档里的规范、被命名和结构化的概念。但你在工作中所展现的价值，大部分是隐性的——源于多年的实践积累。</span><span data-lake-id=\"u2f3c4394\" id=\"u2f3c4394\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">它更像是一个个人的知识图谱：有些是公开的，但很多是你独有的。比如你做决策背后隐藏的逻辑，或者是那种能告诉你“这样做才对”但又无法完全向人解释清楚的直觉。如果你不能把这些传递出去，AI 产出的结果就会十分平庸。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ue0a029d0\" id=\"ue0a029d0\"><span data-lake-id=\"u925ebe7e\" id=\"u925ebe7e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">这里 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6a9b0f5c\" id=\"u6a9b0f5c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">3C 框架</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u005356ac\" id=\"u005356ac\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">非常管用：背景 (Context)、组件库 (Components)、评判标准 (Criteria)。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u4aced710\" id=\"u4aced710\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1776950897636-99a7af28-ceff-41be-98e3-eccf892808b3.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ua9bef48a-2838-47a8-869a-97120c5797f%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22ud56835bc-3d36-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A700%2C%22height%22%3A394%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A202731%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1400%2C%22originHeight%22%3A788%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22OHTENT%20THE%20WOILD%20AL%20STEPS%20INTO.%20OMFOHEHTS%20THE%20TOOLS%20AL%20WORKS%20WITH%2C%20RITERIA%20THE%20STANDARD%20AL%20IS%20HELD%20TO%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A222%2C%22y%22%3A135%2C%22width%22%3A226%2C%22height%22%3A55%2C%22text%22%3A%22OHTENT%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A177%2C%22y%22%3A214%2C%22width%22%3A293%2C%22height%22%3A24%2C%22text%22%3A%22THE%20WOILD%20AL%20STEPS%20INTO.%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A217%2C%22y%22%3A362%2C%22width%22%3A389%2C%22height%22%3A55%2C%22text%22%3A%22OMFOHEHTS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A175%2C%22y%22%3A439%2C%22width%22%3A300%2C%22height%22%3A30%2C%22text%22%3A%22THE%20TOOLS%20AL%20WORKS%20WITH%2C%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A220%2C%22y%22%3A594%2C%22width%22%3A239%2C%22height%22%3A51%2C%22text%22%3A%22RITERIA%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A173%2C%22y%22%3A668%2C%22width%22%3A333%2C%22height%22%3A31%2C%22text%22%3A%22THE%20STANDARD%20AL%20IS%20HELD%20TO%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%2322201f%22%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u857241fa%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><ul list=\"u0e9d02ad\"><li fid=\"ucca59dad\" data-lake-id=\"ub6e9bcab\" id=\"ub6e9bcab\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8be7864d\" id=\"u8be7864d\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">背景 (Context) 是 AI 能看到的一切。</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uffec27bf\" id=\"uffec27bf\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\"> 你需要传递</span><span data-lake-id=\"ub5da9f03\" id=\"ub5da9f03\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"background-color: #FBDE28\">项目的完整背景</span><span data-lake-id=\"ubc29d3a5\" id=\"ubc29d3a5\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">——你在做什么，为谁而做，有哪些限制，已经做出了哪些决定。对于进行中的项目，我会</span><span data-lake-id=\"u77595b0c\" id=\"u77595b0c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"background-color: #FBDE28\">在项目文件夹里留一个 Context 文件，让 AI 每次会话时读取，并随着项目进展不断更新。</span></li><li fid=\"ucca59dad\" data-lake-id=\"ud5e9620b\" id=\"ud5e9620b\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u85aa7870\" id=\"u85aa7870\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">组件 (Components) 是你交给 AI 去干活的工具。</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf7a4bb03\" id=\"uf7a4bb03\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\"> 大模型内置了推理和检索能力，但对于专业工作（代码审查、前端设计、单元测试），它们需要更具体的脚手架。这时候你需要</span><span data-lake-id=\"u01d493c1\" id=\"u01d493c1\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"background-color: #FBDE28\">引入合适的 Skills 或配置 MCP (Model Context Protocol)</span><span data-lake-id=\"uaf436046\" id=\"uaf436046\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">。核心在于：永远不要假设 AI 已经具备了完成任务所需的一切。你必须给它递扳手。</span></li><li fid=\"ucca59dad\" data-lake-id=\"ueb21db43\" id=\"ueb21db43\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u0540c4a7\" id=\"u0540c4a7\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">标准 (Criteria) 定义了输出的质量。</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub2a670aa\" id=\"ub2a670aa\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\"> 不仅要告诉 AI “生成什么”，更重要的是告诉它“不要生成什么”。反向约束往往比正向指令更有效。为格式、样式和准确度设定具体标准，并内置一个让 AI 自我评估的机制。生成 UI 后，我会让它自查：它是不是默认用了蓝紫色调？是不是直接用了 Arial 字体？通过快速自审来过滤掉“AI 味”浓厚的废料。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u3b89abe1\" id=\"u3b89abe1\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud8ace229\" id=\"ud8ace229\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">有了这三层的支撑，你脑海中那些难以言传的判断标准，就能被清晰地传递出去。你会发现输出质量有了肉眼可见的提升。</span></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"Hl7vU\" id=\"Hl7vU\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9e47ed95\" id=\"u9e47ed95\">亲自跑一遍代码 ↘</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u871037e0\" id=\"u871037e0\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub698d09d\" id=\"ub698d09d\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">看别人做和自己亲手做，完全是两码事。现在满大街都是 AI 教程，但真正学到东西的唯一途径，就是亲手去构建点什么。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ub912bc83\" id=\"ub912bc83\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1776951019012-fc3d9a5e-4332-4429-84bd-96e2ed9e641e.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ub394bf70-d3f9-4de5-95ac-5c237c9226e%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22ud56835bc-3d36-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A700%2C%22height%22%3A342%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A478632%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1400%2C%22originHeight%22%3A683%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22ITERATION%20OUTPUT%20INPUT%20RATE%20%26%20PROMPT-TO-%20CREATE%20A%20REFINE%20*%20BASELINE%20*%20PROMPT%20-%20%20ON%20TOP%20OF%20THE%20BASELINE%2C%20%20USE%20A%20SIMPLE%20NATURAL-%20%20USE%20THAT%20AI-GENERATED%20MAKE%20%20PROMPT%20TO%20BUILD%20THE%20FIRST%20%20RATE%20THE%20RESULT%20AND%20ADD%20LANGUAGE%20PROMPT%20TO%20LET%20AI%20%20CLEAN%20VERSION%20OF%20THE%20SCREEN%20GUIDANCE%20TO%20ITERATE%20WRITE%20A%20HIGH-QUALITY%20FIGMA%20MORE%20IMPROVE%20THE%20DESIGN.%20MAKE%20PROMPT%20FOR%20YOU.%20YOUR%20BASELINE%20LAYOUT.%20AND%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A956%2C%22y%22%3A68%2C%22width%22%3A136%2C%22height%22%3A27%2C%22text%22%3A%22ITERATION%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A530%2C%22y%22%3A69%2C%22width%22%3A91%2C%22height%22%3A26%2C%22text%22%3A%22OUTPUT%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A95%2C%22y%22%3A69%2C%22width%22%3A77%2C%22height%22%3A26%2C%22text%22%3A%22INPUT%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A956%2C%22y%22%3A135%2C%22width%22%3A174%2C%22height%22%3A59%2C%22text%22%3A%22RATE%20%26%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A93%2C%22y%22%3A136%2C%22width%22%3A332%2C%22height%22%3A71%2C%22text%22%3A%22PROMPT-TO-%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A527%2C%22y%22%3A141%2C%22width%22%3A235%2C%22height%22%3A52%2C%22text%22%3A%22CREATE%20A%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A954%2C%22y%22%3A199%2C%22width%22%3A259%2C%22height%22%3A73%2C%22text%22%3A%22REFINE%20*%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A525%2C%22y%22%3A202%2C%22width%22%3A325%2C%22height%22%3A69%2C%22text%22%3A%22BASELINE%20*%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A95%2C%22y%22%3A205%2C%22width%22%3A296%2C%22height%22%3A70%2C%22text%22%3A%22PROMPT%20-%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A956%2C%22y%22%3A451%2C%22width%22%3A297%2C%22height%22%3A29%2C%22text%22%3A%22%20ON%20TOP%20OF%20THE%20BASELINE%2C%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A93%2C%22y%22%3A452%2C%22width%22%3A271%2C%22height%22%3A27%2C%22text%22%3A%22%20USE%20A%20SIMPLE%20NATURAL-%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A524%2C%22y%22%3A452%2C%22width%22%3A339%2C%22height%22%3A25%2C%22text%22%3A%22%20USE%20THAT%20AI-GENERATED%20MAKE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A523%2C%22y%22%3A486%2C%22width%22%3A325%2C%22height%22%3A30%2C%22text%22%3A%22%20PROMPT%20TO%20BUILD%20THE%20FIRST%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A955%2C%22y%22%3A486%2C%22width%22%3A301%2C%22height%22%3A31%2C%22text%22%3A%22%20RATE%20THE%20RESULT%20AND%20ADD%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A96%2C%22y%22%3A489%2C%22width%22%3A323%2C%22height%22%3A24%2C%22text%22%3A%22LANGUAGE%20PROMPT%20TO%20LET%20AI%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A524%2C%22y%22%3A521%2C%22width%22%3A351%2C%22height%22%3A27%2C%22text%22%3A%22%20CLEAN%20VERSION%20OF%20THE%20SCREEN%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1018%2C%22y%22%3A522%2C%22width%22%3A249%2C%22height%22%3A27%2C%22text%22%3A%22GUIDANCE%20TO%20ITERATE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A93%2C%22y%22%3A523%2C%22width%22%3A339%2C%22height%22%3A26%2C%22text%22%3A%22WRITE%20A%20HIGH-QUALITY%20FIGMA%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A956%2C%22y%22%3A528%2C%22width%22%3A54%2C%22height%22%3A18%2C%22text%22%3A%22MORE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1007%2C%22y%22%3A556%2C%22width%22%3A244%2C%22height%22%3A28%2C%22text%22%3A%22IMPROVE%20THE%20DESIGN.%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A92%2C%22y%22%3A556%2C%22width%22%3A259%2C%22height%22%3A25%2C%22text%22%3A%22MAKE%20PROMPT%20FOR%20YOU.%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A549%2C%22y%22%3A557%2C%22width%22%3A270%2C%22height%22%3A28%2C%22text%22%3A%22YOUR%20BASELINE%20LAYOUT.%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A956%2C%22y%22%3A561%2C%22width%22%3A41%2C%22height%22%3A20%2C%22text%22%3A%22AND%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23953429%22%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uddb906b1%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u5de51535\" id=\"u5de51535\"><span data-lake-id=\"u288efe45\" id=\"u288efe45\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">具体来说：让 AI 生成项目架构，观察它是如何组织文件和模块的。让它写测试用例，看看它如何处理边缘场景。顺着报错信息往下扒，直到你真正看懂它在抱怨什么。当你把这套流程从头到尾跑通一次后，你会发现你之前对技术的很多恐惧，其实都是自己想象出来的。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u5113a229\" id=\"u5113a229\"><span data-lake-id=\"u014d3d53\" id=\"u014d3d53\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">更重要的是——你只有在做具体事情的过程中，才能总结出普适的规律。举个例子：当一个 Agent 卡在一个 Bug 里无限死循环时，你可以引入另一个 AI 来提供新视角，从而打破失败循环。这种判断力虽然可以向他人学习，但更多时候只能靠自己摸爬滚打积累下来。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ue79c21e3\" id=\"ue79c21e3\"><span data-lake-id=\"u93629a5b\" id=\"u93629a5b\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">在用这种“凭直觉编程” (vibe-coding) 的方式做了五个产品之后，你会开始感受到一种隐约的“材料质感”。这本质上就是建立在各种状态 (States) 之上的肌肉记忆。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22NINSu%22%7D\"></card><h1 data-lake-id=\"iOkO3\" id=\"iOkO3\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua42edc89\" id=\"ua42edc89\">二、重塑设计流程</span></h1><p data-lake-id=\"u291ec944\" id=\"u291ec944\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc2029540\" id=\"uc2029540\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">Claude 的设计负责人 Jenny Wen 在 Lenny’s Podcast 上提出，传统的设计流程——调研、发散、收敛、交付——已经死亡。具体体现在：</span></p><ul list=\"ub773031a\"><li fid=\"ud7d6057a\" data-lake-id=\"u0f5c0743\" id=\"u0f5c0743\"><span data-lake-id=\"u01b8bdb7\" id=\"u01b8bdb7\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">工程开发的速度已经远超线性的设计工作流。</span></li><li fid=\"ud7d6057a\" data-lake-id=\"u761ba078\" id=\"u761ba078\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud68590d9\" id=\"ud68590d9\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">设计师不再有时间去“死磕”静态的视觉规范。</span></li><li fid=\"ud7d6057a\" data-lake-id=\"uaeb2b2f1\" id=\"uaeb2b2f1\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc3450c29\" id=\"uc3450c29\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">画饼式的长周期“设计愿景”变得不再切合实际。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"udbbe9986\" id=\"udbbe9986\"><span data-lake-id=\"u892c8a37\" id=\"u892c8a37\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">从这个角度看，设计流程的死亡，似乎是被</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8fb92f7c\" id=\"u8fb92f7c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">工程团队呈指数级膨胀的执行力</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1b8dc9ee\" id=\"u1b8dc9ee\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">倒逼出来的——当然，这其中也掺杂了一点科技圈惯有的夸张。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uc8dac253\" id=\"uc8dac253\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc03c3634\" id=\"uc03c3634\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">传统的“发散-收敛”流程其实并没有完全失效。问题在于，它建立在一个前提之上：由于制作高保真原型或 Demo 的成本极高，因此在进入下一步之前，每一步都需要大量的全盘准备。而现在，这个前提不复存在了。</span></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"unyKI\" id=\"unyKI\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc9477577\" id=\"uc9477577\">直觉 → Demo → 必然性 ↘</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u0d06e640\" id=\"u0d06e640\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubf3e968a\" id=\"ubf3e968a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">过去，严谨的前期调研是刚需，因为做一个能用来验证的东西太贵了。现在这个成本无限趋近于零。整个游戏的玩法全变了。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u1934d688\" id=\"u1934d688\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf57e233c\" id=\"uf57e233c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">经验丰富的产品思考者完全可以凭直觉快速生成一个 Demo，然后用这个 Demo 来压力测试自己的判断——而不是一群人围在白板前，为了“这个方向到底对不对”而纸上谈兵。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ue04fb6a7\" id=\"ue04fb6a7\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1776951142436-070755b0-4077-470e-8b67-950facdc7a40.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u545bf2a6-1c55-4a2c-a8e1-06e07500c8f%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22ud56835bc-3d36-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A700%2C%22height%22%3A345%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A262529%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1400%2C%22originHeight%22%3A689%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22AURA%20OF%20IHEVITAEILITY%20IF%20SOMETHING%20EXISTS%20IN%20CODE%20AND%20IT'S%20ALREADY%20BASICALLY%20THERE%2C%20IT'S%20DIFFICULT%20TO%20SAY%2C%20'NO%2C%20WE%20SHOULDN'T%20DO%20THIS%2C%20'%20YOU%20KNOW%3F%20IT'S%20LIKE%2C%20NO%2C%20IT'S%20BASICALLY%20%3A%20ALREADY%20THERE%20LIKE%2CLET'S%20JUST%20MAKE%20IT%20HAPPEN%20CLEO%20DESIGNER%20AT%20FACEBOOK%20DIVE%20CLUB%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A219%2C%22y%22%3A162%2C%22width%22%3A686%2C%22height%22%3A48%2C%22text%22%3A%22AURA%20OF%20IHEVITAEILITY%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A222%2C%22y%22%3A250%2C%22width%22%3A1046%2C%22height%22%3A49%2C%22text%22%3A%22IF%20SOMETHING%20EXISTS%20IN%20CODE%20AND%20IT'S%20ALREADY%20BASICALLY%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A221%2C%22y%22%3A305%2C%22width%22%3A1018%2C%22height%22%3A47%2C%22text%22%3A%22THERE%2C%20IT'S%20DIFFICULT%20TO%20SAY%2C%20'NO%2C%20WE%20SHOULDN'T%20DO%20THIS%2C%20'%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A222%2C%22y%22%3A354%2C%22width%22%3A712%2C%22height%22%3A52%2C%22text%22%3A%22YOU%20KNOW%3F%20IT'S%20LIKE%2C%20NO%2C%20IT'S%20BASICALLY%20%3A%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A946%2C%22y%22%3A363%2C%22width%22%3A265%2C%22height%22%3A35%2C%22text%22%3A%22ALREADY%20THERE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A223%2C%22y%22%3A409%2C%22width%22%3A259%2C%22height%22%3A47%2C%22text%22%3A%22LIKE%2CLET'S%20JUST%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A493%2C%22y%22%3A415%2C%22width%22%3A322%2C%22height%22%3A40%2C%22text%22%3A%22MAKE%20IT%20HAPPEN%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1234%2C%22y%22%3A527%2C%22width%22%3A64%2C%22height%22%3A24%2C%22text%22%3A%22CLEO%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1031%2C%22y%22%3A557%2C%22width%22%3A266%2C%22height%22%3A27%2C%22text%22%3A%22DESIGNER%20AT%20FACEBOOK%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1178%2C%22y%22%3A591%2C%22width%22%3A120%2C%22height%22%3A22%2C%22text%22%3A%22DIVE%20CLUB%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23cfcfce%22%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22udb940b05%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u270ec682\" id=\"u270ec682\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufba03b7e\" id=\"ufba03b7e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">更关键的是，一个能在真实浏览器里跑起来的 Demo，带有一种特殊的说服力。前 Facebook 设计师 Cleo 称之为“必然性光环” (Aura of Inevitability)。当一个设计概念不再是干瘪的静态视觉稿，而是由真实代码构建、能跑能动的东西时，它就产生了一种引力。在这种情况下，团队很难再去争论“要不要推进它”——因为它几乎已经做出来了。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uebcc283f\" id=\"uebcc283f\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3c792b7c\" id=\"u3c792b7c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">大家最自然的反应会是：这玩意我们大概率可以直接上线。 静态文件做不到这一点，只有跑得通的真实原型才有这样的分量。</span></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"g1zm8\" id=\"g1zm8\"><span data-lake-id=\"uee3a2293\" id=\"uee3a2293\">回归第一性原理 ↘</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u0bae0b4d\" id=\"u0bae0b4d\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud544c946\" id=\"ud544c946\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">在 AI 出现之前，大多数设计师很少有机会触及软件在更深层面是如何运作的。我们主要在抽象层工作：视觉、交互、信息架构。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u48f88d87\" id=\"u48f88d87\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua6fc5d84\" id=\"ua6fc5d84\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">这是一个巨大的门槛落差。 仅仅是把设计做好、把原型连好，就已经耗尽了我们能支配的大部分精力。根本没有余力去深挖底层。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uce4e3072\" id=\"uce4e3072\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue7e01fb5\" id=\"ue7e01fb5\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">AI 改变的正是这种精力分配比。它把“怎么做出来”的成本压缩到了接近零，从而把时间和认知资源还给了设计师。我们现在可以将更多精力投入到那个最根本的问题上：</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u9df3619d\" id=\"u9df3619d\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">这个东西到底应该是什么？</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"u49e73fb8\" id=\"u49e73fb8\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1776951243284-edacdc06-f1ca-45f9-aafc-8cf292cbcbdd.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u03488d71-62b3-4fef-bd03-6de99c418a2%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22ud56835bc-3d36-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A700%2C%22height%22%3A362%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A240306%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1400%2C%22originHeight%22%3A723%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22NOTION%20CURSOR%20TIKTOK%20AA%20%E7%9B%AE%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A628%2C%22y%22%3A101%2C%22width%22%3A160%2C%22height%22%3A50%2C%22text%22%3A%22NOTION%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1044%2C%22y%22%3A105%2C%22width%22%3A164%2C%22height%22%3A45%2C%22text%22%3A%22CURSOR%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A216%2C%22y%22%3A106%2C%22width%22%3A155%2C%22height%22%3A46%2C%22text%22%3A%22TIKTOK%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A599%2C%22y%22%3A278%2C%22width%22%3A52%2C%22height%22%3A36%2C%22text%22%3A%22AA%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A606%2C%22y%22%3A403%2C%22width%22%3A41%2C%22height%22%3A44%2C%22text%22%3A%22%E7%9B%AE%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23d5cbca%22%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ueed83bd0%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u795b6bcb\" id=\"u795b6bcb\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3f97afde\" id=\"u3f97afde\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">当你开始认真思考“它到底是什么”时，你的第一性原理思维就会变得极其锐利。这个问题有两层含义。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ue0c7a9e2\" id=\"ue0c7a9e2\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u7e7a4c61\" id=\"u7e7a4c61\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">第一层是产品的核心概念</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u60b86d22\" id=\"u60b86d22\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">——也就是软件呈现自身的底层形态。TikTok 的底层是一个自动循环的视频列表；Notion 的核心是 Block（页面和数据库）；Cursor 的核心是 Agent、编辑器和模型。这些概念听起来很简单。但只有看透了它们，你才能在各种功能之间找到最精简、最灵活的连接点。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u6a6179b0\" id=\"u6a6179b0\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5638fb2f\" id=\"u5638fb2f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">第二层是推演</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc112d121\" id=\"uc112d121\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">：一旦你理解了基石，你就可以开始推演一个产品理想中该长成什么样。这是从内部生长出来的核心逻辑，而不是对照着竞品的功能清单打勾，在别人的地图里做选择题。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u5962d281\" id=\"u5962d281\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3bacdf31\" id=\"u3bacdf31\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">这种认知维度的提升，给了设计师真正的空间，去探索一个产品在其能力边界上到底能走多远。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22dfiUx%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"4746b6f3\" id=\"4746b6f3\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubbbd6e5e\" id=\"ubbbd6e5e\">三、搭建你自己的“脚手架”</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"ue5c39be9\" id=\"ue5c39be9\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9d97c1ca\" id=\"u9d97c1ca\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">每个设计师都会在工作流中遇到阻力，遇到工具不趁手的时候。过去我们的选择是：要么忍着，要么用人工填补这些坑。指望市面上马上出现一个完美的新工具简直是奢侈。大多数时候，你只能将就。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ue99a088e\" id=\"ue99a088e\"><span data-lake-id=\"u36df6648\" id=\"u36df6648\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">但现在，设计师可以自己动手搭建工具了——为了眼前的特定任务，低成本定制一套专属的脚手架。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u5744da75\" id=\"u5744da75\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1776951278645-0b91a177-6ce8-40b6-be7e-4d810d67bf73.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u2c44bf29-4db1-4491-9086-67502a77693%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22ud56835bc-3d36-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A700%2C%22height%22%3A381%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A347142%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1400%2C%22originHeight%22%3A761%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22FIGMA%20MAKE%20LCON%20LIBRARY%20DOCUMENTATION%20SITE%20B%20C%20AL%20LCON%20LIBRARY%20DOCUMENT...%20SHARE%20HOME%20C%20LCON%20LIBRARY%20PROJECT%20GOAL%20BUILD%20A%20CLEAN%2CPRODUCTION-READY%20'LCON%20LCONS%20GUIDELINES%20LIBRARY%20DOCUMENTATION%20SITE%20THAT%20LETS%20USERS%20BROWSE%20COMMONLY%20USED%20ICONS%20(INSPIRED%20BY%20MATERIAL%20DESIGN)%2CFILTER%20BY%20CATEGORIES%20SEARCH%20ICONS...%20CATEGORY.PREVIEW%20AT%20MULTIPLE%20SIZES%20(40%2C24%2C16.12%20PX)%2CAND%20DOWNLOAD%20EACH%20ICON%20AS%20PNG%20AND%20SVG.THE%20SITE%20MUST%20SHOWING95%20ICONS%2014%20NAVIGATION%20BE%20FAST%2CACCESSIBLE(WCAG%202.1AA).%20PREVIEW%20%20SIZE%20RESPONSIVE%2CAND%20EASY%20TO%20EXTEND.%2016%20ACTIONS%2040PX%20AUDIENCE%26TONE%2024PX%2016PX%2012PX%2015%20MEDIA%20UX%2FUL%20DESIGNERS%20AND%20FRONT-END%20ENGINEERS.NEUTRAL%2CCONCISE%202PX%20STROKE%20%20WIDTH%2012%20COMMUNICATION%20DOCUMENTATION%20TONE.ALL%