22ubab124f1%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u7fdf6d89\" id=\"u7fdf6d89\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue48d8e6e\" id=\"ue48d8e6e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">拿我自己的例子来说：过去找图标意味着每次都要在网上像无头苍蝇一样搜寻。这是典型的重复性精力内耗。 后来，我直接用 Figma Make 建了一个专属的图标库，把全网的开源图标集整合在一起，加上了对颜色、粗细和风格的控制器，还能直接导出 PNG 或 SVG。过去每次都要经历的折磨，现在变成了一劳永逸。这是最小单位的脚手架，但它确确实实彻底消灭了这一步的阻力。</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22plain%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E7%BA%A7%E5%88%AB%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BE%E6%A0%87%E5%BA%93%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E7%AB%99%E7%82%B9%E3%80%82%5Cn%23%23%20%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%A0%88%20React%20%2B%20TypeScript%20%C2%B7%20Tailwind%20CSS%20v4%20%C2%B7%20shadcn%2Fui%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20lucide-react%20%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%20UI%20%C2%B7%20%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%20WCAG%202.1%20AA%20%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%20%C2%B7%20%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E7%AB%AF%E4%BC%98%E5%85%88%5Cn%23%23%20%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%5Cn1.%20%E7%BA%A6%20100%20%E4%B8%AA%E5%9B%BE%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%208%20%E4%B8%AA%E7%B1%BB%E5%88%AB%EF%BC%88UI%E4%B8%8E%E5%AF%BC%E8%88%AA%E3%80%81%E9%80%9A%E8%AE%AF%E3%80%81%E5%AA%92%E4%BD%93%E3%80%81%E7%94%B5%E5%95%86%E3%80%81%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E3%80%81%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%94%E3%80%81%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E3%80%81%E6%9D%82%E9%A1%B9%EF%BC%89%5Cn2.%20%E6%A8%A1%E7%B3%8A%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%20%2B%20%E5%A4%9A%E9%80%89%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E8%BF%87%E6%BB%A4%E5%99%A8%5Cn3.%20%E5%B0%BA%E5%AF%B8%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E5%99%A8%20(12%2F16%2F24%2F40px)%20%2B%20%E6%8F%8F%E8%BE%B9%E7%B2%97%E7%BB%86%E6%BB%91%E5%9D%97%20(1%E2%80%933px)%5Cn4.%20%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B6%20SVG%20%2F%20JSX%20%C2%B7%20%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%8D%95%E5%9B%BE%E6%A0%87%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%20PNG%20%2F%20SVG%5Cn5.%20%E4%BA%AE%E8%89%B2%20%2B%20%E6%9A%97%E8%89%B2%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%88%E8%B7%9F%E9%9A%8F%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%81%8F%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%89%5Cn6.%20%E5%8C%85%E5%90%AB%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83%E3%80%81%E6%97%A0%E9%9A%9C%E7%A2%8D%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E5%92%8C%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%5Cn%23%23%20%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%20%E9%A1%B6%E9%83%A8%E5%90%B8%E9%A1%B6%E5%AF%BC%E8%88%AA%20%C2%B7%20%E5%B8%A6%E6%9C%89%E7%B1%BB%E5%88%AB%E8%AE%A1%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%A7%E8%BE%B9%E6%A0%8F%20%C2%B7%20%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E6%A0%8F%20%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E5%BC%8F%E5%9B%BE%E6%A0%87%E7%BD%91%E6%A0%BC%20(1%E2%86%922%E2%86%924%20%E5%88%97)%20%C2%B7%20%E9%A1%B5%E8%84%9A%20v1.0.0%5Cn%23%23%20%E5%9B%BE%E6%A0%87%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%7B%20id%2C%20name%2C%20category%2C%20tags%5B%5D%2C%20svg%20(24%C3%9724%20viewBox)%20%7D%5Cn%23%23%20%E4%BA%A4%E4%BB%98%E7%89%A9%20%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E7%AB%99%E7%82%B9%20%C2%B7%20%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%20%C2%B7%20%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%95%B4%E6%B4%81%E5%B9%B6%E5%85%B7%E5%A4%87%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E6%8E%A8%E6%96%AD%20%E6%97%A0%E9%9C%80%E5%90%8E%E7%AB%AF%20%C2%B7%20%E6%98%93%E4%BA%8E%E6%89%A9%E5%B1%95%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E5%9B%BE%E6%A0%87%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22default%22%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22FkVgv%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card><p data-lake-id=\"ucfc39e8d\" id=\"ucfc39e8d\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"udce8398d\" id=\"udce8398d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u51ab1327\" id=\"u51ab1327\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">Cursor 的设计负责人 Ryo Lu 也做了类似的事情，只是规模更大。他提到设计师经常被复杂的后端服务和生产环境卡住——于是他为自己造了一个 </span><em><span data-lake-id=\"u3658b1d8\" id=\"u3658b1d8\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">Baby Cursor</span></em><span data-lake-id=\"u93b16068\" id=\"u93b16068\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">：一个高度简化、去繁就简的沙盒（微型环境）。在这个环境里，他可以不受任何技术牵绊地快速验证想法。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u14f50f92\" id=\"u14f50f92\"><span data-lake-id=\"u659df71f\" id=\"u659df71f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">这里的通用原则是：</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5b89facf\" id=\"u5b89facf\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">当你发现工作流中的某一步在不断消耗你的精力，且具有高度重复性时，这就是一个信号——该造工具了。</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6f1d0d79\" id=\"u6f1d0d79\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\"> 花一次性的成本把它搭起来，之后省下来的所有时间，你都可以用来做更高级的判断和创作。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u7d923f12\" id=\"u7d923f12\"><span data-lake-id=\"uabb47b70\" id=\"uabb47b70\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">过去这要求你必须懂代码。现在，这个壁垒已经荡然无存。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u43ccbc13\" id=\"u43ccbc13\"><span data-lake-id=\"u482e05e3\" id=\"u482e05e3\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">写到这里，我意识到我通篇都在用不同的方式表达着同一个观点：</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u34795a07\" id=\"u34795a07\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u50f0f428\" id=\"u50f0f428\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"background-color: #FBDE28\">AI 并没有让设计师变得不重要。相反，它让“这位设计师是谁”变得比以往任何时候都更加重要。</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"ud83a0b60\" id=\"ud83a0b60\"><span data-lake-id=\"u69d423d4\" id=\"u69d423d4\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">任何人都可以使用这些工具。但你能用它们造出什么，完全取决于你是一个怎样的人。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u6b156409\" id=\"u6b156409\"><span data-lake-id=\"u669f2155\" id=\"u669f2155\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">​</span><br></p><blockquote data-lake-id=\"u15d46cd4\" id=\"u15d46cd4\"><p data-lake-id=\"ua8520946\" id=\"ua8520946\"><span data-lake-id=\"ude380f4e\" id=\"ude380f4e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">原文链接：</span><a href=\"https://uxdesign.cc/becoming-an-ai-native-designer-828365b71109\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u8aa361ba\" id=\"u8aa361ba\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4d95b6eb\" id=\"u4d95b6eb\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">https://uxdesign.cc/becoming-an-ai-native-designer-828365b71109</span></a></p></blockquote>"}
